author: Trumbull Times
title: Girls volleyball: Eagles sweep Hilltoppers
text:
By Trumbull Times on October 19, 2015 in FCIAC , High School Sports , Sports Features · 0 Comments 
The Trumbull High girls volleyball team defeated Bridgeport Central 25-10, 25-13, 25-14 on Monday. 
Sydney Adams had 27 assists and 8 aces. Liv Borski had 4 kills, 6 digs and 6 aces. 
Lauren Zielinski had 9 service points with two aces and two digs. 
Ges Scaccia had 7 kills and two blocks. 
For Central, Kimberly Keller had 3 service points, 2 blocks and an ace. Tarah Bernard had 3 service points, a kill and two aces. Related posts:
